{{#if (or person.isAlpha person.isProspective)}}
  Information about Work Access Passes will be made avaible in June or July. Please check back at that time.
{{else}}
  {{#if ticketPackage.tickets}}
  <h4 class="text-success">
     Hooray! You have
    {{#if (eq ticketPackage.tickets.length 1)}}
      a ticket
    {{else}}
      {{ticketPackage.tickets.length}} tickets
    {{/if}}
    available:
  </h4>
    <ul>
      {{#each ticketPackage.tickets as |ticket|}}
        <li>A {{ticket-type-human ticket.type}} earned in {{ticket.source_year}} and will expire after {{mdy-format ticket.expiry_date}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>
    <strong>What happens next?</strong>
    <p>
      There is nothing you need to do at this time.
      Information about how to claim your Reduced Price Ticket (RPT) or Staff Credential (SC) will be
      available in the Clubhouse in June or early July. If you are not planning on atttending
      the Burn this year, you may bank the ticket(s).
    </p>
  {{else}}
    <strong>Sorry, it doesn't appear you qualified for a Reduced-Price Ticket or Staff Credential.</strong>
    <p>
      You earned {{credits-format ticketPackage.credits_earned}} last event. The minimum credits needed to earn
      a Reduced-Price Ticket was {{credits-format ticketingInfo.rpt_credits}}, and a Staff Credential was
      {{credits-format ticketingInfo.sc_credits}}.
    </p>
  {{/if}}

  <strong>Where are the Vehicle and Work Access Passes?</strong>
  <p>
    Don't worry, vehicle passes &amp; WAPs will be made available in the coming months.
    An announcement will be made in June or July on when you will be able to claim
    the passes.
  </p>
{{/if}}
